articles.title: ENG vs AUS, 3rd Ashes Test, Day 2 Highlights: Four-Down Australia Lead England By 142 Runs At Stumps.. - NDTV Sports
articles.description: ENG vs AUS, 3rd Ashes Test, Day 2 Highlights: Australia were four down at Stumps on Friday with a lead of 142 runs. The side's score read 116 for 4 when the play on Day 2 was called off.
